  (entity 'arm (x 0 y 0))
  (entity 'hand (rotation 0))
  (timeline
    (at 0.0
      (ease 'arm 'x 0 90 0.5 'cubic-out)
      (ease 'arm 'y 0 -10 0.5 'cubic-out)
      (ease 'hand 'rotation 0 -10 0.5 'cubic-out))
    (at 0.5
      (hold 0.8))))
```

[VISUAL: Arm extends forward and slightly upward, hand rotates to open palm, holds.]

A gentle reach. The long hold (0.8 seconds) is an *offering*—\"take this\" or \"come with me.\"

