### The Tentative Reach

Extend partway, pause, complete:

```scheme
(motion
  (entity 'arm (x 0))
  (timeline
    (at 0.0
      (ease 'arm 'x 0 50 0.4 'cubic-out))
    (at 0.4
      (hold 0.5))
    (at 0.9
      (ease 'arm 'x 50 90 0.3 'cubic-out))
    (at 1.2
      (hold 0.6))))
```

[VISUAL: Arm extends halfway, pauses, then extends fully.]

The mid-reach pause is *hesitation*—\"should I?\"

