      (ease 'head 'rotation 0 5 0.5 'cubic-out))
    (at 0.5
      (hold 0.8))))
```

[VISUAL: Torso shifts backward and tilts away, head tilts back, holds.]

The backward lean is *creating distance*. Head tilt back adds to the sense of withdrawal.

